title: The all-new Google Pixel Buds Pro with ANC arrive in July for $199
content:
After a major leak last week, Google has finally announced the latest addition to its wireless earbuds hardware lineup, the Pixel Buds Pro. The earbuds will be available in four colors, come priced at $199, and will go on sale starting in July. The Pixel Buds Pro are Google’s latest foray into the world of

The post The all-new Google Pixel Buds Pro with ANC arrive in July for $199 appeared first on XDA.
description: The Google Pixel Buds Pro were announced today, delivering big sound and ANC in a compact package. The earbuds will arrive in July for $199.
